# Markdown++
Is a transpiled language for writing documentations implemented in JavaScript embedding the [Gyro](https://continuum-ai.de/docs/gyro) language.

![A screenshot of Markdown++ code](/assets/code-screenshot.png)

{{table}}

## Features
Since Markdown++ is transpiled it allows for some features not possible in the orignal [Markdown](https://markdown.de/) language, like:

- !`Auto Link Resolving`